    AdminActivity3
    Admin Activity allows the user to specify another filter for the data logs - by regions
    AdminActivityFinal

    Diagnosis Activity 2 that asks for further symptoms the person in peril may have The symptoms in this page is generated dynamically based on Diagnosis Activity 1
